4Geeks Academy offers a Cybersecurity Bootcamp designed for aspiring cybersecurity specialists, requiring no prior knowledge. The program spans 16 weeks with three live online classes per week, accommodating up to 16 students per class. Participants gain foundational skills in Windows, Linux, networking, and server administration, alongside training in cloud security, penetration testing, and cyber threat intelligence. The bootcamp also emphasizes risk management and compliance with international standards like ISO 27001 and NIST. Graduates earn an official 4Geeks Completion Certificate, recognized by various institutions. The program is available in both English and Spanish. For more information, visit [4Geeks Academy](https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/cybersecurity). stop